                WARNING: HIGH RADIATION DETECTED
              </span>
           </div>
           <div className="mt-2 text-[9px] text-stone-600 font-mono">
              SECURE CONNECTION: ENCRYPTED (AES-4096)
           </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
